Working Process
User registers and logs in.

The app displays nearby heritage locations.

User visits a selected location.

The camera scans a QR code or image marker.

AR content appears on the screen.

The user receives a clue or puzzle.

After solving it, the next location is unlocked.

The process continues until the treasure hunt is completed.

The final score and rewards are displayed.

